name: I Say Goodbye To The Rotten World
description:
This work is an art for people living in this era.
And it’s convey this history to the future.

This work has audio.
This is a valuable announcement of Japan's "state of emergency".

It's important to confront the chaos without escaping. However, when it's hard, it's also important to stop and rest.

Gentle people who think about others and limit their freedom.
I want all those people to release their minds in the world of art.

It is a work that combines such wishes with reality.
